		<title>Zipline to build 12 new hubs as Nigeria becomes its biggest African market</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/05/28/zipline-targets-100-million-nigerians-with-12-new-hubs-by-2028/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Frank Eleanya]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 09:50:16 +0000</pubDate>
