		<title>4 easy steps to move your ChatGPT memory to Claude </title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/05/27/4-easy-steps-to-move-your-chatgpt-memory-to-claude/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Fancy Goodman]]></dc:creator>
